title: The Blackpool Gazette & Herald
abstract: The Blackpool Gazette & Herald (1874 - 1919) was a weekly newspaper which has been digitised by the British Library for the Living with Machines project
library_of_congress_classification_1: The file consists of the OCR (Optical Character Recognition) text in XML format for one year of Blackpool Gazette & Herald. The full digitised newspapers comprises 1183-1198, 1215-2310 (22 May-4 Sept. 1874; 1 Jan. 1875-12 May 1893); no. 2311-5160 (19 May 1893-30 Dec. 1919) The newspaper continued beyond 1919, but this has not been digitised. The digitised page images for years 1874 - 1919 are available on the British Newspaper Archive website, https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/titles/blackpool-gazette--herald The newspaper beyond 1879, but this has not been included in the dataset due to copyright considerations. The British Newspaper Archive pages images are behind a paywall, but from March 2021 the paywall will be lifted and some of these images will be free to view.
